CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 22, 1967, pg. 16 reads: "Pennsylvania State Association of Beauticians and Beauty Shop Owners met in quarterly session at the Penn Sheraton Hotel April 2nd...Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group of women, including one wearing light colored top with scarf, gathered in Penn Sheraton Hotel for the Pennsylvania State Association of Beauticians and Beauty Shop Owners quarterly session
